[Cepat!]

254
00:16:34,600 --> 00:16:36,120
[Cepat sikit!]

255
00:16:37,720 --> 00:16:38,520
Saya

256
00:16:38,960 --> 00:16:39,880
dan semua orang

257
00:16:40,840 --> 00:16:43,360
sangat mengalu-alukan awak

258
00:16:43,440 --> 00:16:44,600
untuk menyertai

259
00:16:44,600 --> 00:16:46,760
Jabatan Pemantauan Penangkapan Penjenayah.

260
00:16:47,480 --> 00:16:48,880
Selamat datang.

261
00:16:48,880 --> 00:16:50,560
- Selamat datang.
